# Post-Edit Verification

After editing any `.ts` file, follow the "Post-Edit Verification" checklist in `CONTRIBUTING.md`.

Quick summary:
1. Run lints on edited files
2. Verify `.js` extensions on relative imports
3. Verify `import type` for type-only imports
4. No `console.*` — use `logger` from `@alerthq/core`
5. Error message prefixes in plugins: `[provider-id]`
6. New files must be kebab-case
